## Getting the Token from the Control Center

1. Log in to the Barracuda Control Center.
2. Navigate to the **Connect Products** page.
3. Copy the **validation token**.

[Find more details here](https://campus.barracuda.com/product/webapplicationfirewall/doc/96013142/connecting-the-barracuda-web-application-firewall-to-the-barracuda-waf-control-center)

